6. the person who's hobby is camping is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the person who's hobby is board-games##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |   3    |     4      |   5    |    6    |   7    |
| Hobby   | filmmaking | video-games | camping | board-games | skydiving | reading | writing |

